\c 9
\s Ukuthunywa kwabaphostoli
\p
\v 1 Wasebizela ndawonye abafundi bakhe abalitshumi lambili\x + Mat. 10.1.\x*, wabanika amandla legunya phezu kwamadimoni wonke, lawokwelapha izifo\x + Mat. 10.5,7,8. Mark. 6.7. Luka 10.1,9.\x*.
\v 2 Wasebathuma uku\add ya\add*tshumayela umbuso kaNkulunkulu, lokusilisa abagulayo,
\v 3 wasesithi kubo: Lingaphathi lutho lwendlela; lodondolo, lesikhwama, lomphako, lemali, njalo lingabi lezigqoko ezimbili ngamunye.
\v 4 Lakuyiphi indlu elingena kuyo, hlalani lapho, lalapho lisuke\x + Mat. 10.9-14. Mark. 6.8-11. Luka 10.4-11.\x*.
\v 5 Labo bonke abangalemukeliyo, nxa lisuka kulowomuzi, thintithani ngitsho uthuli enyaweni zenu kube yibufakazi obumelana labo\x + Mat. 8.4.\x*.
\v 6 Basuka-ke bahamba bedabula imizana, betshumayela ivangeli besilisa endaweni zonke\x + Mark. 6.12.\x*.
\s Ukubulawa kukaJohane uMbhabhathizi
\p
\v 7 UHerodi \w umtetrarki\w**\x + 9.9. 3.1.\x* wasekuzwa konke okwenziwa nguye\x + Mat. 14.1-3. Mark. 6.14-16.\x*; wasedideka\x + 24.4. Seb. 2.12. 5.24. 10.17.\x*, ngoba kwatshiwo ngabanye ukuthi uJohane uvukile kwabafileyo;
\v 8 langabanye ukuthi uElija ubonakele; langabanye ukuthi kuvukile omunye wabaprofethi abadala.
\v 9 Kodwa uHerodi wathi: UJohane ngamquma ikhanda mina; kodwa ngubani lo, mina engizwa ngaye izinto ezinje? Wasefunisisa ukumbona\x + 23.8.\x*.
\s UJesu usuthisa amadoda azinkulungwane ezinhlanu
\p
\v 10 Abaphostoli\x + Mark. 6.30.\x* sebebuyile bambikela konke ababekwenzile. Wasebathatha\x + Mat. 14.13-21. Mark. 6.32-44. Joha. 6.1-13.\x*, wahamba labo bebodwa waya endaweni eyinkangala eyomuzi othiwa yiBhethisayida\x + Mark. 6.45.\x*.
\v 11 Kwathi amaxuku esekwazi, amlandela; wasewemukela, wakhuluma lawo ngombuso kaNkulunkulu\x + Mark. 6.34.\x*, wabasilisa labo abaswele ukusiliswa\x + Mat. 14.14.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Ilanga laseliqala ukutshona\x + 24.29.\x*; abalitshumi lambili basebesiza bathi kuye: Yekela ixuku lihambe, ukuze baye emizaneni lezigabeni ezizingelezeleyo bangenise \add khona\add*, bathole ukudla\x + 19.7.\x*; ngoba lapha sisendaweni eyinkangala.
\v 13 Kodwa wathi kubo: Banikeni lina bona ukuthi badle. Bathi-ke: Asilakho okwedlula izinkwa ezinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili, ngaphandle kokuthi thina siyebathengela ukudla bonke lababantu.
\v 14 Ngoba kwakukhona amadoda angaba zinkulungwane ezinhlanu. Wasesithi kubafundi bakhe: Bahlaliseni phansi ngezigaba ngamatshumi amahlanu.
\v 15 Basebesenza njalo, babahlalisa phansi bonke.
\v 16 Wasezithatha izinkwa ezinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili, wakhangela phezulu ezulwini, wazibusisa, wa\add zi\add*hlephula, wa\add zi\add*nika abafundi ukuthi babeke phambi kwexuku.
\v 17 Basebesidla basutha bonke; kwadojwa imvuthu ezazisele kubo, izitsha ezilitshumi lambili.
\s Isivumo sokholo sikaPetro. UJesu ukhuluma ngokufa lokuvuka kwakhe
\p
\v 18 Kwasekusithi ekhuleka yedwa, abafundi babelaye; wasebabuza, esithi: Amaxuku athi ngingubani\x + Mat. 16.13-16. Mark. 8.27-29.\x*?
\v 19 Basebephendula bathi: UJohane uMbhabhathizi; kodwa abanye \add bathi\add*: UElija; kodwa abanye \add bathi\add*: Kuvukile umprofethi othile wabadala\x + Joha. 6.14.\x*.
\v 20 Wasesithi kubo: Lina-ke lithi ngingubani? UPetro wasephendula wathi: UKristu kaNkulunkulu.
\v 21 Esebaxwayisisile\x + Mark. 8.30. Mat. 16.20.\x* walaya ukuthi bangatsheli muntu lokhu\x + Mat. 12.16.\x*,
\v 22 esithi\x + Mat. 16.21-28. Mark. 8.31; 9.1.\x*: INdodana yomuntu imele ihlupheke kakhulu, ilahlwe ngabadala labapristi abakhulu lababhali, ibulawe, ibisivuswa ngosuku lwesithathu\x + Mat. 17.22,23. Luka 9.43,44.\x*.
\s Ukuhlutshwa kukaJesu lokwabamlandelayo
\p
\v 23 Wasesithi kubo bonke: Uba umuntu ethanda ukuza ngemva kwami, kazidele, athathe isiphambano sakhe\x + Mat. 10.38.\x* insuku ngensuku, angilandele\x + 1 Kor. 15.31.\x*.
\v 24 Ngoba loba ngubani othanda ukusindisa impilo yakhe, izamlahlekela; kodwa loba ngubani olahlekelwa yimpilo yakhe ngenxa yami, yena uzayisindisa.
\v 25 Ngoba kuzamsizani umuntu, uba ezuza umhlaba wonke, kodwa yena uqobo lwakhe azone kumbe alahleke\x + Mat. 16.26. Mark. 8.36. 1 Kor. 3.15. 2 Kor. 7.9. Fil. 3.8.\x*?
\v 26 Ngoba loba ngubani olenhloni ngami langamazwi ami, iNdodana yomuntu izakuba lenhloni ngaye, nxa isiza enkazimulweni yayo lekaBaba leyengilosi ezingcwele.
\v 27 Kodwa ngilitshela ngeqiniso: Bakhona abanye kwabemiyo lapha, abangasoze bezwe ukufa, baze babone umbuso kaNkulunkulu.
\s Ukukhazimuliswa kukaJesu entabeni
\p
\v 28 Kwasekusithi\x + Mat. 17.1-8. Mark. 9.2-8.\x* emva kwalawomazwi\x + 9.44.\x*, kungaba zinsuku eziyisificaminwembili\x + Mat. 17.1. Mark. 9.2.\x*, wathatha uPetro loJohane loJakobe, wakhwela entabeni uku\add ya\add*khuleka\x + 3.21. 6.12. Mat. 14.23.\x*.
\v 29 Kwasekusithi ekukhulekeni kwakhe, isimo sobuso bakhe saphenduka, lesembatho sakhe saba mhlophe, sacwazimula\x + Mark. 16.12.\x*.
\v 30 Njalo khangela, akhuluma laye amadoda amabili, ayengoMozisi loElija\x + 9.30,34.\x*;
\v 31 abonakala ngenkazimulo\x + 9.32. 2.9. Joha. 1.14.\x* akhuluma ngokusuka kwakhe ayezakuphelelisa eJerusalema\x + 2 Pet. 1.15.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa uPetro lababelaye babesindwe yibuthongo\x + Dan. 8.18. 10.9. Mat. 26.43. Mark. 14.40.\x*; kodwa sebephapheme babona inkazimulo yakhe\x + 9.32. 2.9. Joha. 1.14.\x*, lamadoda amabili ayemi laye.
\v 33 Kwasekusithi, ekwehlukaneni kwawo laye\x + 9.30,34.\x*, uPetro wathi kuJesu: Nkosi\x + 9.49. 5.5.\x*, kuhle ukuthi sibe lapha; futhi asakhe amadumba amathathu, elinye ngelakho, lelinye ngelikaMozisi, lelinye ngelikaElija; engakwazi akutshoyo\x + Mark. 9.6.\x*.
\v 34 Kwathi ekhuluma lezizinto, kwafika iyezi labasibekela; basebesesaba ekungeneni kwabo eyezini\x + 9.30,34.\x*.
\v 35 Kwasekuphuma ilizwi eyezini, lisithi: Lo uyiNdodana yami ethandekayo; zwanini yona.
\v 36 Kwathi ilizwi selifikile, uJesu waficwa eyedwa. Kodwa bona bathula, kabaze batshela muntu ngalezonsuku okunye kwalezozinto abazibonileyo\x + Mat. 17.9. Mark. 9.9.\x*.
\s Ukusiliswa komfana owayelesithuthwane
\p
\v 37 Kwasekusithi ngelanga elilandelayo, sebehlile\x + Mat. 17.14-18. Mark. 9.14-27.\x* entabeni, ixuku elikhulu lamhlangabeza\x + 9.28.\x*.
\v 38 Njalo khangela, indoda exukwini yamemeza, isithi: Mfundisi, ngiyakuncenga, bona indodana yami\x + 1.48.\x*, ngoba \add yiyo\add* yodwa ezelweyo yami\x + 7.12.\x*;
\v 39 njalo khangela, umoya uyayibamba, futhi ihle iklabalale\x + Seb. 8.7.\x*, njalo uyihlukuze, ikhihlize amagwebu, uphume nzima kuyo, uyihluzule\x + Mark. 1.26.\x*.
\v 40 Njalo ngincenge abafundi bakho ukuthi bawukhuphe, kodwa abenelisanga.
\v 41 UJesu wasephendula wathi: O sizukulwana esingelakholo lesonakeleyo, kuzaze kube nini ngilani, ngilibekezelela? Ilethe lapha indodana yakho.
\v 42 Kuthe iseza, idimoni layidabula la\add yi\add*hlukuza; kodwa uJesu wawukhuza umoya ongcolileyo, wamsilisa umntwana, wambuyisela kuyise.
\s UJesu uphinda akhulume ngokuhlupheka kwakhe
\p
\v 43 Bonke basebemangaliswa kakhulu yibukhulu bukaNkulunkulu. Kwathi bemangele bonke ngazo zonke izinto uJesu azenzileyo, wathi kubafundi bakhe\x + Mat. 17.22,23. Mark. 9.30-32. Luka 9.22.\x*:
\v 44 Fakani lina endlebeni zenu lamazwi\x + 21.14. 1.66.\x*: Ngoba iNdodana yomuntu izanikelwa ezandleni zabantu.
\v 45 Kodwa kabaqedisisanga lumutsho, njalo wawufihlakele kubo, ukuze bangawuzwisisi; basebesesaba ukumbuza ngalumutsho\x + Mark. 9.32. Luka 2.50. 18.34. Joha. 12.16.\x*.
\s UJesu ufundisa ngokuthobeka
\p
\v 46 Kwasekungena\x + Mat. 18.1-5. Mark. 9.34-37.\x* ukuphikisana phakathi kwabo, ukuthi ngubani ongaba mkhulu kubo\x + 2.35.\x*.
\v 47 Kwathi uJesu ebona ukunakana kwenhliziyo yabo\x + Mat. 9.4. Mat. 18.1.\x*, wathatha umntwana omncane, wammisa phansi kwakhe,
\v 48 wasesithi kubo: Loba ngubani owemukela lumntwana omncane ebizweni lami wemukela mina; njalo loba ngubani owemukela mina wemukela ongithumileyo\x + Mat. 10.40.\x*; ngoba omncinyane kini lonke nguye ozakuba mkhulu\x + Mat. 23.11. Luka 22.26.\x*.
\p
\v 49 UJohane wasephendula wathi\x + 9.49,50, Mark. 9.38-40.\x*: Nkosi, sabona omunye ekhupha amadimoni ngebizo lakho, sasesimenqabela, ngoba engalandeli kanye lathi.
\v 50 Kodwa uJesu wathi kuye: Linga\add m\add*enqabeli, ngoba ongamelani lathi ungakithi\x + 9.33.\x*.
\s UJesu uyasuka aye eJerusalema
\p
\v 51 Kwathi seziphelelisiwe insuku\x + Seb. 2.1.\x* zokwenyuka kwakhe\x + Mark. 16.19. Seb. 1.2,11,22. 1 Tim. 3.16.\x*, yena wasekhangelisa ubuso bakhe ukuya eJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 8.11. 12.17. Mark. 10.32. Luka 12.50.\x*,
\v 52 wasethuma izithunywa phambi kobuso bakhe\x + 10.1.\x*; zasezihamba zangena emzaneni\x + Mat. 10.5.\x* wamaSamariya\x + 1 Kho. 16.24.\x*, ukuze zimlungisele.
\v 53 Kodwa kawamemukelanga\x + Joha. 4.45.\x*\x + Joha. 4.4,9,27.\x*, ngoba ubuso bakhe babukhangele eJerusalema\x + 2 Lan. 32.2.\x*.
\v 54 Kwathi abafundi bakhe uJakobe loJohane\x + Mark. 3.17.\x* bebona \add lokhu\add* bathi: Nkosi, uyathanda yini ukuthi sitsho ukuthi umlilo wehle uvela ezulwini, ubaqothule, njengoba loElija wenza\x + 2 Kho. 1.10,12.\x*?
\v 55 Kodwa watshibilika wabakhuza, esithi: Alazi ukuthi lina lingabomoya onjani.
\v 56 Ngoba iNdodana yomuntu kayizanga ukuthi ibhubhise imiphefumulo yabantu, kodwa uku\add yi\add*sindisa\x + Mat. 18.11. Joha. 8.11.\x*. Basebesedlulela komunye umzana.
\s Ukulandela uJesu
\p
\v 57 Kwasekusithi behamba endleleni\x + 9.51.\x*, \add umuntu\add* othile wathi kuye: Nkosi, ngizakulandela loba ngaphi lapho oya khona.
\v 58 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Amakhanka alemilindi, lenyoni zezulu \add zile\add*zidleke; kodwa iNdodana yomuntu kayilalapho engaqamelisa ikhanda khona\x + Mat. 8.19-22.\x*.
\v 59 Wasesithi komunye: Ngilandela. Kodwa yena wathi: Nkosi, ngivumela ukuthi ngiyengcwaba ubaba kuqala.
\v 60 Kodwa uJesu wathi kuye: Yekela abafileyo bangcwabe ababo abafileyo; kodwa wena hamba utshumayele umbuso kaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 8.21.\x*.
\v 61 Lomunye wasesithi: Ngizakulandela, Nkosi\x + 1 Kho. 19.20.\x*; kodwa ngivumela kuqala ukuthi ngiyevalelisa abasendlini yami\x + Mark. 6.46. Luka 14.33. Seb. 18.18,21. 2 Kor. 2.13.\x*.
\v 62 Kodwa uJesu wathi kuye: Kakho othi esebeke isandla sakhe ekhubeni, akhangele kokusemuva\x + 10.2.\x*, ofanele umbuso kaNkulunkulu\x + 14.35. Heb. 6.7.\x*.
